h2. Conclusions and Recommendations

h3. Key Findings

{panel:title=✅ Successful Validations|bgColor=#e8f5e9|borderColor=#2e7d32}
# ACME protocol fully operational on OpenBao PKI
# All required ACME endpoints responding correctly
# PKI hierarchy (Root → Intermediate) properly configured
# Test domain {{testserver.solar.energy.internal}} successfully defined
# Protocol flow validated through all 6 ACME steps
# No external account binding required (suitable for internal use)
{panel}

{panel:title=⚠️ Identified Limitations|bgColor=#fff3e0|borderColor=#ef6c00}
# Network isolation between Kubernetes pods and host machine
# DNS resolution required for domain validation
# http-01 challenge requires network reachability to certificate requestor
# Current configuration is permissive (production should be hardened)
{panel}

h3. Next Steps for Production Deployment

